OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny patchy cloud will clear
OL,6,Fquickly, leaving another bright and
OL,7,Fsunny day. Turning hazier from the
OL,8,Fsouth through the afternoon. Winds
OL,9,Flighter than Wednesday allowing
OL,10,Ftemperatures to climb further.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA clear night to start with
OL,13,Flight winds, but patchy cloud
OL,14,Fdeveloping in the east. Some mist and
OL,15,Ffog forming in prone clear spots, with
OL,16,Fa grass frost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
